        <item>
            <title>Casio 停止開發電子辭典新產品，平板電腦普及令需求急劇減少</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/17/casio-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=casio-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/17/casio-2/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 06:30:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CASIO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電子辭典]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1292081</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本 Casio 近日宣佈將停止電子辭典的新產品開發。該公司指，市場對於電子辭典的需求急劇減少，並提到智能手機和學校中平板電腦的普及是主要原因之一。雖然停止新產品的開發，現有的電子辭典仍將繼續生產和銷售。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292084" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202521701screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202521701screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202521701screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202521707screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202521707screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202521707screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在 1981 年，Casio 推出了首款電子辭典，開創了這一市場並成功建立了「Ex-word」品牌。根據 BCN 總研的調查，去年 Casio 在日本國內電子辭典市場佔有約 80% 的份額。隨著智能手機的普及以及學校平板電腦的應用，電子辭典的需求逐漸減少。Casio 表示，這是停止新產品開發的主要原因。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292086" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025217013screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025217013screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025217013screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292087" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025217020screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025217020screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025217020screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Casio 強調現有電子辭典的生產和銷售將繼續進行，並未完全退出市場。公司計劃將資源轉向其他領域，以應對當前的市場變化和需求。</p><p>Casio 這次決定反映出，科技和教育工具的迅速發展，以及市場需求的轉變，一些傳統科技日漸被取代。雖然電子辭典的市場逐漸萎縮，Casio 仍將繼續在現有產品上保持其市場地位。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_14790"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IfcMJD6P9jQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p data-start="415" data-end="489">資料來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IfcMJD6P9jQ">ANNNews</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
