        <item>
            <title>NBA 引入 AI 機械人，Stephen Curry 率先體驗智能射波訓練</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/17/nba-ai-robots-training/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nba-ai-robots-training</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/17/nba-ai-robots-training/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 05:38:41 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[nba]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1291632</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>NBA 於鹽湖城展示最新 AI 機械人技術，並邀請金州勇士隊球星 Stephen Curry 率先試用。Stephen Curry 在訓練時使用名為 ABE（Automated Basketball Engine） 的機械人作為投籃夥伴，ABE 機械人可以自動執波、亦設有精準傳球功能，使球員能全神貫注於投籃訓練。Stephen Curry 最初對這項高科技設備感到新奇，但旋即適應，並認為表示機械人無須飲水休息，可以幫助球員進行更加高強度的訓練。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1292070 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Stephen Curry 使用 ABE 機械人協助訓練，圖片來源：<a href="http://youtube.com/watch?v=iwp7HbfNsp4&amp;ab_channel=NBA">NBA@YouTube</a></p><p>Golden State Warriors 主教練 Steve Kerr 亦引入 MIMIC（Motion &amp; Intercept Modular-Interface Coordination） 機械人，協助球員模擬比賽中的進攻與防守戰術。這款機械人可精確追蹤球員的細微動作，模仿防守者的壓迫感，並即時提供反饋，讓教練團隊得以因應情境調整戰術，強化球員臨場應變能力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292071" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MIMIC，圖片來源：<a href="http://youtube.com/watch?v=iwp7HbfNsp4&amp;ab_channel=NBA">NBA@YouTube</a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1292072" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/adamsilverandgoldens-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MIMIC 可在訓練期間模擬人類球員進攻、防守等動作，圖片來源：<a href="http://youtube.com/watch?v=iwp7HbfNsp4&amp;ab_channel=NBA">NBA@YouTube</a></p><p>NBA 透過今次機械人技術測試，展現人工智能於體育領域的潛力。隨着技術持續發展，球員與教練團隊或許能在不久將來見證更多 AI 投入訓練與比賽分析，進一步提升球場表現，為籃球運動開啟新篇章。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_71080"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iwp7HbfNsp4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://interestingengineering.com/innovation/basketball-robot-stephen-curry-shooting-partner">Interesting Engineer</a>、<a href="https://www.techspot.com/news/106788-stephen-curry-new-shooting-partner-robot-never-gets.html">Tech Spot</a>、 <a href="https://technology.inquirer.net/140724/nba-debuts-ai-robots-as-stephen-currys-shooting-partner">Technology Inquirer</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
